  • Method Details

    • apply

      public java.lang.Boolean apply​(Data data)

      Applies this filter to Data instance passed ad argument. It compares specified field value of the data instance to the value stored inside this filter instance.

      For instance, with "greater" operator it returns true if specified field of the provided Data instance is greater that value stored

      Parameters:
      data - Data object to which apply this filter
      Returns:
      A boolean, result of the comparision
